#OMShanti Soldier Medical Assistant Sergeant Shri Surendra Kumar Moga attained Veergati guarding air base after Pakistani drone strike in J&K's Udhampur on 10 May early morning.
Originally posted in Bengaluru, he had been redeployed to Udhampur just four days ago due escalating tensions with Pakistan.
Moga's Family in Mehradasi Village of Rajasthan 's Jhunjhunu was informed on Saturday. He is Survived by his 65 Years old Mother Nanu devi, wife seema devi and Two Children. Villagers gathered to Mourn as preperation began for a state funeral. He is a native of Mandawa in Rajasthan's Jhunjhunu.
RIP Braveheart •
